,"uid":79081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"成篇文吹到外賣好好景<br />\n連50歲前企業高層都去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完完全全想水人入行<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔流失率高，無待遇又要求多多<br />\n一個鐘得一單，而家一單30蚊都冇<br />\n又要行樓梯搵路<br />\n<br />\n搵得多只係某幾件<br />\n大撚把人一個月開行晒turbo 10k都無<br />\n步兵行撚到腳斷點樣日日行<br />\n<br />\n馬死落地行都絕對唔係送外賣賺果1個鐘2x蚊<br />\n<br />\n呢期D外賣公司出盡奶力做PR<br />\n又東張西望又愛回家<br />\n又出埋D廢文話好境<br />\n咪撚比PR公司水入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb613f4a7e7d472b6850bf9852a9036b9e6f094","tid":2159491,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8354de4795e9c7de2c5be95ea9a2b58f1e2237c9","tid":2159491,"uid":79081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"成篇文吹到外賣好好景<br />\n連50歲前企業高層都去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完完全全想水人入行<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔流失率高，無待遇又要求多多<br />\n一個鐘得一單，而家一單30蚊都冇<br />\n又要行樓梯搵路<br />\n<br />\n搵得多只係某幾件<br />\n大撚把人一個月開行晒turbo 10k都無<br />\n步兵行撚到腳斷點樣日日行<br />\n<br />\n馬死落地行都絕對唔係送外賣賺果1個鐘2x蚊<br />\n<br />\n呢期D外賣公司出盡奶力做PR<br />\n又東張西望又愛回家<br />\n又出埋D廢文話好境<br />\n咪撚比PR公司水入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味 俾班失業大軍加公司害死"},{"pid":"548ce9cc5c5c5c53b44f4748b4aa822236cf8a2c","tid":2159491,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"外賣仔搵得多嗰班一定係揸電單車嗰班 步兵搵得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cd74248a2d31c9db2d4e4e63f5818f88df880c","tid":2159491,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8354de4795e9c7de2c5be95ea9a2b